dc_title_s: Planta Rex do Distrito Federal organizada no escritorio té́cnico Milton Ferreira de Carvalho com elementos do seu cadastro imobiliário, especialmente para o Guia Rex, indicador geral do Rio de Janeiro
dc_description_s: Topographic map with street names, roads, and railroads. Relief is shown by contours. Oriented with north to the lower right. Map is missing sheet 2 covering two eastern sections: Estaç̃ao Santa Cruz to Senador Camará ; Estaç̃ao de Pavuna to Auxiliary Line. "Propriedade de Geddes & Guillou." Lewis Map and Geospatial Information Center does not have the companion directory.
